Key Features of the BMG Warehouse Stock Management System:
Professional BMG-Themed Interface

Uses BMG's blue and orange color scheme

Clean, modern design with intuitive navigation

Stock Verification System

Search by part number or stock code

Shows current bin location vs correct bin location

Clear visual indicators for correct/incorrect placement

Dashboard Overview

Key metrics at a glance

Stock accuracy rate tracking

Discrepancy alerts

Bin Location Guidance

Clear instructions for correct placement

Zone identification for easier navigation

Visual status indicators

Responsive Design

Works on desktop and mobile devices

Accessible for warehouse staff on the go

The system helps prevent stock loss by ensuring items are always placed in their correct bin locations and provides immediate feedback to employees during stock checks.